com.github.fge.jsonschema.schema

Class SchemaContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.fge.jsonschema.schema.SchemaContext
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CanonicalSchemaContext, InlineSchemaContext

    public abstract class SchemaContext
extends Object
    A JSON Schema context

    A schema context contains the JSON representation of a schema, plus its location (as a JsonRef).

    This class embodies the ability to tell whether a JSON reference is embodied within the schema itself. It is particularly important for AddressingMode.INLINE addressing mode.
